This map is the classic ze map,and original map.
1 round's play time until humans win needs about 7 minutes.
There are little dangerous trap.
For example,if humans fall into hole,they will die directly.

Map info :
Console command : mp_roundtime 10
THERE IS NO ITEM.
AND DON'T HAVE SOME DIFFICULTY.
3 Late teleport points.


If you found the bug of this map,please report me.
